    • updateCloudletProcessing

      protected void updateCloudletProcessing()
      从类复制的说明: PowerContainerDatacenter
      Updates processing of each cloudlet running in this PowerDatacenter. It is necessary because Hosts and VirtualMachines are simple objects, not entities. So, they don't receive events and updating cloudlets inside them must be called from the outside.
      覆盖:
      updateCloudletProcessing 在类中 PowerContainerDatacenter

    • processVmCreate

      protected void processVmCreate​(SimEvent ev, boolean ack)
      从类复制的说明: ContainerDatacenter
      Process the event for a User/Broker who wants to create a VM in this PowerDatacenter. This PowerDatacenter will then send the status back to the User/Broker.
      覆盖:
      processVmCreate 在类中 ContainerDatacenter
      参数:
      ev - a Sim_event object
      ack - the ack
